sql.up: CREATE TABLE stories (id text NOT NULL DEFAULT 'story_'::text || xata_private.xid()::text, user_id text NOT NULL, title text NOT NULL, description text, xata_id text NOT NULL DEFAULT 'rec_'::text || xata_private.xid()::text, xata_version int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, xata_createdat timestamptz(6) NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp, xata_updatedat timestamptz(6) NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp, CONSTRAINT stories_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id))
